com.elvenrings.qdemo.model

Class FillBlankQuestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.elvenrings.qdemo.model.Question
      • com.elvenrings.qdemo.model.FillBlankQuestion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Questionable

    public class FillBlankQuestion
extends Question
implements Questionable
    A Question implementation class which accepts a string or series of strings as possible answers for the question it poses. In more technical terms this means that its encapsulated Choice member variable is of type FillBlank
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
